@startuml UC-TL-04: Manage Project Members

actor "Team Leader" as TL
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "ProjectController" as API
participant "ProjectService" as Svc
database "project_members / users" as DB

TL -> FE: Chọn DA → "Quản lý thành viên"
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/projects/{id}
API --> FE: Project + members list

== Thêm Member ==

TL -> FE: Tìm NV cùng phòng ban → Nhấn "Thêm"
FE -> API: POST /api/v1/projects/{id}/members {userId}
API -> Svc: addMember(projectId, userId)
Svc -> DB: save(ProjectMember, role=MEMBER)
Svc --> API: ProjectMember
API --> FE: 201
FE --> TL: Thêm thành viên thành công

== Xóa Member ==

TL -> FE: Chọn Member → Nhấn "Xóa"
FE -> API: DELETE /api/v1/projects/{id}/members/{userId}
API -> Svc: removeMember(projectId, userId)
Svc -> Svc: check userId != leaderId

alt Xóa chính Leader
    Svc --> API: throw Forbidden
    API --> FE: 400 Không thể xóa Leader
else OK
    Svc -> DB: delete(ProjectMember)
    Svc --> API: success
    API --> FE: 200
end

@enduml
